The paper discusses multiple instance learning (MIL) which is a subfield of machine learning. MIL has been applied in various application fields such as computer vision (cs.CV), document classification (cs.IR), and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the characteristics of MIL problems, which are relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
